text: Bartosz Machaj (born 30 April 1993) is a Polish footballer who plays as a midfielder for Elana Toruń. ==Career== On 22 June 2019 Elana Toruń confirmed, that they had signed Machaj on a one-year contract.BARTOSZ MACHAJ KOLEJNYM NABYTKIEM ELANY, elanatorun.com, 22 June 2019 ==External links== * * ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders Category:Polish footballers Category:Ekstraklasa players Category:I liga players Category:II liga players Category:Śląsk Wrocław players Category:Miedź Legnica players Category:Chrobry Głogów players Category:Elana Toruń players Category:People from Głogów Category:Sportspeople from Lower Silesian Voivodeship
